            "content": {
                "type": "steps",
                "items": [
                    "Begin by standing with your feet hip-width apart and your arms at your sides.",
                    "Lift your right foot off the ground and cross it over your left thigh, placing your right ankle on top of your left knee.",
                    "Bend your left knee and lower your hips down towards the ground, keeping your back straight and your chest lifted.",
                    "Place your hands on your hips or bring them together in front of your heart.",
                    "Hold the pose for 5-10 breaths, then release and repeat on the other side."
